* [[Ammiak]]an molekul NH<sub>3</sub>
* [[Almaz]] C — tetraedr 2,5220 angstremad kül'genke
* [[Flüorit]] CaF<sub>2</sub> — tetraedr 3,8626 angstremad kül'genke
* [[Sfalerit]] ZnS — tetraedr 3,823 angstremad kül'genke
* [[Kompleksine ion|Kompleksižed ionad]] [BF<sub>4</sub>] <sup>-</sup>, [ZnCl<sub>4</sub>]<sup>2-</sup>, [Hg(CN)<sub>4</sub>]<sup>2-</sup>, [Zn(NH3)<sub>4</sub>]<sup>2+</sup>
* [[Silikatad]] — niiden aluses om tetraedranvuitte ion olanke da hapanikanke [SiO<sub>4</sub>]<sup>4-</sup>

